```tactics
import Mathlib

/-- A derivation tree for a context-free derivation step.
  This is a generalization of a binary tree for an arbitrary number of children.
  Each node has a value (a symbol from the context-free grammar) and a list of children.
  The root of the tree corresponds to the initial word of the derivation.
  Each step of the derivation corresponds to a new level of the tree.
